msgid "The Drowned City"
msgstr "淹灭之城"

msgid "Alien Glyphs"
msgstr "异星字符"

msgid "Task progress"
msgstr "任务进度"

msgid "Artifacts Earned"
msgstr "取得的神器"

msgid "Locations of R'lyeh"
msgstr "拉莱耶地点"

msgid "Flooded Neighborhoods"
msgstr "淹没的街区"

msgid "Artifacts"
msgstr "神器"

msgid "Relentless"
msgstr "无情"

msgid ""
"“... the nightmare corpse-city of R’lyeh, that was built in measureless aeons behind history by the vast, loathsome shapes that seeped down from the dark stars. There lay great Cthulhu and his hordes, hidden in green slimy vaults and sending out at last, after cycles incalculable, the thoughts that spread fear to the dreams of the sensitive and called imperiously to the faithful to come on a pilgrimage of liberation and restoration.”\n"
"<right>–H. P. Lovecraft, “The Call of Cthulhu“</right>"
msgstr ""
"“……梦魇死城拉莱耶，是由黑暗群星上渗透下来的可憎巨怪在史前难以衡量的亘古筑成。伟大的克苏鲁与其部属长眠于此，隐匿在绿色粘液的墓穴中。在无数个轮回之后，它们最终将心思远播，给敏感之人的梦境带来了恐惧，不可违逆地呼唤忠实的信徒踏上解放与归位的朝圣之旅。”\n"
"<right>——H.P.洛夫克拉夫特，《克苏鲁的呼唤》</right>"


msgid "<i>I want to drift</i>"
msgstr "我就随波逐流"

msgid "<i>I want to dream</i>"
msgstr "我只沉眠入梦"

msgid "<i>I want to dive</i>"
msgstr "我偏沉入深海"

msgid "<i>I want R'lyeh</i>"
msgstr "我愿去拉莱耶"

msgid "One First Last Job"
msgstr "（第一次）金盆洗手"

msgid "Complete <i>The Drowned City</i> campaign once on any difficulty."
msgstr "完成任意难度的<i>《淹灭之城》</i>剧本一次。"

msgid "Season Two"
msgstr "第二季"

msgid "Play through the campaign on hard or expert mode using 4 investigators from 4 different previous campaigns."
msgstr "使用4位分别来自先前4个不同的剧本的调查员，在困难或专家模式下，进行本剧本的游戏。口悬崖跳水：不使用潜水服完成本剧本。"

msgid "Cliff Diver"
msgstr "悬崖跳水"

msgid "Complete the campaign without ever bringing a diving suit along."
msgstr "不使用潜水服完成本剧本"

msgid "This is a Coup"
msgstr "造反了"

msgid "Defeat both Naomi O’Bannion and Sadie Sheldon in <i>One Last Job</i> using only the act 3a parley ability."
msgstr "在<i>“金盆洗手”</i>中，只使用场景3a的谈判能力将内奥米·欧巴尼恩和萨迪·谢尔顿都击败。"

msgid "Thorough Search"
msgstr "查个清楚"

msgid "End <i>The Western Wall</i> with every location revealed."
msgstr "<i>“西墙”</i>结束时每个地点都已揭示。"

msgid "Tidal Flip Minigame"
msgstr "潮汐小游戏"

msgid "Complete <i>The Drowned Quarter</i> with each location revealed and not flooded."
msgstr "完成<i>“溺亡城区”</i>且每个地点都已揭示、未淹没。"

msgid "No Acolyte Left Behind"
msgstr "祭司救星"

msgid "Rescue 5 cultists in <i>The Apiary</i>."
msgstr "在<i>“养育场”</i>中拯救5个异教徒。"

msgid "Kill the Adds"
msgstr "优先转火，别打BOSS"

msgid "Defeat Mother in <i>The Apiary</i> using only her <b>Forced</b> effect."
msgstr "在<i>“养育场”</i>中只使用主母的<b>强制</b>效果将其击败。"

msgid "In The Deep End"
msgstr "深水之城"

msgid "Escape <i>The Grand Vault</i> with the Tidal Tablet after every location has been fully flooded."
msgstr "在<i>“大秘库”</i>中每个地点都完全淹没后带着潮汐碑匾逃脱。"

msgid "Sorry, Didn’t See You There"
msgstr "真没看见"

msgid "Beat <i>Court of the Ancients</i> without moving the Great Lift after the Colossal Tyrant spawns."
msgstr "在<i>“远古宫廷”</i>中，巨型霸王生成后，不移动大升降机而通关。"

msgid "Sky Rider"
msgstr "天空骑士"

msgid "End your turn in open sky at least 5 times during a single game of <i>Obsidian Canyons</i>."
msgstr "一次<i>“黑曜石峡谷”</i>游戏期间，在天空结束你的回合至少5次。"

msgid "Skip to the End"
msgstr "跳至结局"

msgid "Defeat Cthulhu in <i>Sepulchre of the Sleeper</i>."
msgstr "在<i>“沉睡者之陵”</i>中击败克苏鲁。"

msgid "Alien School Dropout"
msgstr "异星辍学生"

msgid "Complete the campaign without translating a single alien glyph."
msgstr "完成本剧本但不翻译任何异星字符。"

msgid "Alien School Graduate"
msgstr "异星毕业生"

msgid "Translate all 26 alien glyphs during a single playthrough of <i>The Drowned City</i> campaign."
msgstr "在一次<i> 《淹灭之城》</i> 剧本期间翻译所有26个异星字符。"

msgid "Empty Handed"
msgstr "两手空空"

msgid "Return from R'lyeh without having collected any [[Artifact]] story assets."
msgstr "从拉莱耶返回却没有收集任何[[神器]]剧情支援。"

msgid "WHY. WON’T. YOU. STAY. DEAD?!"
msgstr "你死不死?!"

msgid "Add The Inescapable to the victory display at least 20 times during a single campaign."
msgstr "在一次剧本期间将穷途异魔加入胜利区至少20次。"

msgid "Finish <i>The Drowned City</i> campaign having earned the following artifacts:"
msgstr "取得以下神器完成<i>《淹灭之城》</i>剧本：："

msgid "Grisly \"Mask\""
msgstr "骇人“面具”"

msgid "Obligations"
msgstr "重担在肩"

msgid "Finish <i>The Drowned City</i> campaign with the following tasks completed:"
msgstr "完成<i>《淹灭之城》</i>剧本并完成下列任务："

msgid "Win <i>The Drowned City</i> campaign with at least three Ultimatums active."
msgstr "在挑战至少三项究极试炼的情况下获得<i>《淹灭之城》</i>剧本的胜利。"

msgid "R’lyeh Expertise"
msgstr "拉莱耶专家"

msgid "Win <i>The Drowned City</i> campaign on Expert difficulty."
msgstr "在专家难度下获得<i>《淹灭之城》</i>剧本的胜利。"
